**RED Phase Documentation:**

**Gap**: The security-test-planner agent (243 lines) exceeds the 200-line agent best practice. Lines 122-213 contain an 84-line embedded Phase 6 test planning workflow with:
- 5-step methodology (load phases, prioritization formula, 4 test categories, priority matrix, summary)
- Detailed artifact schemas and field requirements
