**Problem**: This embedded workflow makes the agent too long and violates the principle of extracting reusable methodology into library skills for reference.

**Test Scenario**: Without this skill, the security-test-planner agent must embed all workflow details inline, causing:
- Agent line count to exceed recommended limits
- Workflow knowledge duplicated if multiple agents need test planning
- Harder to maintain and update test planning methodology
- Reduced agent clarity (methodology embedded vs referenced)

**Solution**: Extract the Phase 6 test planning methodology into this library skill, allowing security-test-planner to reference it via gateway-security routing.

